{"tid":2393787,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"17歲女孩愛上57歲大爺，曾約定生子，7年過去女孩快要認不出了","createTime":"2021-02-03T17:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T02:00:07.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"215f67f488c8d41e141625264d30a70301a539ea","tid":2393787,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"之前網上有人問，大家能接受的最大的年齡差是多少人？大部分人能夠接受的最大年齡差是五歲以內，十歲的話就有點大了，但還是能夠接受的。而超過了十歲，已經不敢想了，畢竟在現實中年齡差超過十歲，家人肯定會有些猶豫的。對於那些年齡差超過十二歲，甚至二十歲的，小編只能說接受無能。而在台灣，有一對年齡差四十歲的情侶，人稱&ldquo;爺孫戀&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2Fb91093cfp00qnstm6005xc000jg00kpm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252Fb91093cfp00qnstm6005xc000jg00kpm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d8c536db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  其實仔細想想可不就是爺孫戀嗎？你十歲的時候對方五十歲，你二十歲的時候對方已經六十歲了，簡直太可怕。但是這對&ldquo;爺孫戀&rdquo;情侶卻非常恩愛，兩個人從女孩子十七歲的時候就在一起了，如今已經過去了七年，他們仍舊是在一起。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2Fe8932653p00qnstm60054c000jg00g8m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252Fe8932653p00qnstm60054c000jg00g8m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=03e5ca9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  女孩子叫林靖恩，原本只是一位17歲的普通女學生，直到她愛上了比自己大40歲的李坤城。李坤城算是有點人氣和錢的，畢竟他也是一位音樂製作人，但是相對來說在台灣比較火，在內地完全沒有他的名字。李坤城和林靖恩的父親是關係不錯的朋友，最初的時候兩個人只是長輩與晚輩之間的相處，後來兩個人產生了感情，便開始瞞著家裡談戀愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2Fde787328p00qnstm60051c000jg00dmm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252Fde787328p00qnstm60051c000jg00dmm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=bdf6b757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  顧忌到林靖恩還沒有成年，所以李坤城和林靖恩在一起的時候，一直都是發乎情而止乎禮的，但是即便如此，仍舊讓林靖恩的父親十分氣憤。有句話怎麼說？我拿你當朋友，你卻想要泡我的女兒？這件事情放在誰身上都會很氣憤，所以林爸爸一氣之下就把李坤城給告了，但是你告了有什麼用呢？林靖恩是自願的，哪條法律規定相差四十歲不能談戀愛？所以即便告了也沒用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2F5f35f20cp00qnstm6008bc000jg00mnm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252F5f35f20cp00qnstm6008bc000jg00mnm.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=bec3f570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  林靖恩十七歲的時候正是叛逆的時候，她覺得自己和李坤城是被外界孤立的一對小情侶，還覺得他們的愛情特別偉大。林靖恩在家裡瘋狂砸東西，美曰其名是&ldquo;為了愛情作鬥爭&rdquo;，林靖恩為了和家人對抗，甚至還鬧自殺，最後父親沒轍了，索性隨他們去了。林靖恩和李坤城的故事還傳到了韓國，這兩個人又火了一把。兩個人在一起之後，經常出去遊玩、爬山，李坤城和林靖恩還約定要一起生個孩子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2Ff6677585p00qnstm6006ic000jg00e3m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252Ff6677585p00qnstm6006ic000jg00e3m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=ca036153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  林靖恩不懂為什麼外界要反對他們在一起，她覺得自己是遇到了真愛。<br />\n<br />\n  其實李坤城這個人十分花心，他曾有一個小20歲的女朋友，直到他愛上了林靖恩，才拋棄了那個小20歲的女朋友。只不過這次變本加厲，找了個小40歲的女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2F24831b33p00qnstm60057c000jg00d4m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252F24831b33p00qnstm60057c000jg00d4m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=4b8575dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  當年，17歲的少女愛上了57歲的大爺，如今已經過去了七年之久，當初的少女卻已經快要認不出了。林靖恩曾說過，自己的男朋友是個&ldquo;老古板&rdquo;，她才二十四歲，而男朋友已經六十多了，兩個人的差距越來越大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2Ffeda5568p00qnstm60053c000jg00d1m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252Ffeda5568p00qnstm60053c000jg00d1m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=21b50741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  這種差距不僅僅是年齡上和外貌上的差距，還有思想上的差距。隨著李坤城年齡的繼續增大，兩個人能在一起的時間也越來越少，就算李坤城能活到100歲，那個時候的林靖恩也才60歲，她下半輩子該怎麼辦呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0131%2F1ca4d470p00qnstm60039c000jg00d9m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0131%252F1ca4d470p00qnstm60039c000jg00d9m.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d5f5d10e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69930f108be994b8435e0eafb421b31a8e932457","tid":2393787,"uid":136377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"AV情節"},{"pid":"1e026ee14ead18db120e3776b0b61a75c478441a","tid":2393787,"uid":123774,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:21:33.000Z","msg":"比隻老坑咁樣屌過<br />\n再靚都只係一隻窿"},{"pid":"6aa3c41026b1da95f0fa7defcbd56dd362737da4","tid":2393787,"uid":113807,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T17:23:33.000Z","msg":"生bb未 想睇"},{"pid":"f7776d474c9a57b4ae60288296d7d274f9b8657a","tid":2393787,"uid":50719,"li